text: Goldbach is a market community in the Aschaffenburg district in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany. ==Politics== ===Community council=== The council is made up of 24 council members, not counting the mayor. CSU SPD FWG Total 2008 9 2 13 24 seats (as at municipal election held on 2 March 2008) ===Town partnerships=== * Courseulles-sur-Mer, Calvados, France since 1994; the commune lies at Juno Beach.
